replies.body:
No problem. 
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 

Please warn your friend that their account is on very thin ice once it's had a 14-day ban - any further punishments, even minor ones that would normally just be a chat restriction, can go straight to a perma-ban. If he can't control his chat he's probably best to mute each game and avoid it entirely.

Oh darn, sorry to hear that :( 
{{sticker:cass-cry}} 
Yeah do tell him - we get a lot of people who don't take the 14-day warning seriously and then come asking why they got perma-banned just for telling someone to stfu.
